# 2025‑10‑24 — LibreOffice Calc Integration Milestone

## Summary
Added an installation automation script for **LibreOffice Calc**, enabling spreadsheet functionality for data analysis and project management on Fedora Asahi systems.

This step integrates GUI productivity software into the system automation stack, complementing existing command‑line workflows.  
Libre Calc supports both quantitative data work for trading analytics and CSV‑driven job‑application tracking.

## Key Highlights
- Introduced `core/scripts/install_libre_calc.sh` for reproducible deployment.
- Verifies installation and version output automatically.
- Demonstrates GUI application management via shell automation.
- Marks a progression checkpoint in the portfolio’s “Essential Admin Tooling” segment.

## Outcome
✅ LibreOffice Calc installed successfully via automated script.  
✅ Fully integrated into the `core/scripts/` directory for public reference.  
✅ System‑wide tool now available for all user profiles.

